Title: S4 EP  178 Best of 2021 Alex Teal & Isabella
Description:
In this week's episode of the Intern Whisper, Isabella talks with one of the video editors of the podcast episodes, Alex Teal.  They discuss Alex's picks for the best of 2021 podcasts: 

Ep. 167 Xaulanda Simmonds-Emmanuel

Ep. 171 Lonnie Snyder

Ep. 175 Jason Krauss

Ep. 177 Kent Gustavson and Randy Baker

They discuss Alex's passion about film, his future projects, and what he thinks the future of the film industry will be.
